  "texts": [
    "Thirdly, the GRU model is applied to the extracted, purified data.",
    "Fourthly, the MLP model is also applied to the extracted, purified data.",
    "Finally, the performance of the proposed system is evaluated using various performance measures like a graphical analysis and a statistical test.",
    "To verify the consistency of the proposed hybrid system, the dataset is trained and tested using three different ratios.",
    "The study's results show that the proposed hybrid system for ETD is highly accurate and efficient compared to other models including Alexnet, GRU, BGRU and RNN."
  ]
